### ========================================
### 35 - Lookup & Reference Data
### Lookup Controller, Service Translations
### ========================================

### ----------------------------------------
### PATIENT LOOKUP
### ----------------------------------------

### Lookup patient by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/lookup/patient/by-email?email=patient@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Lookup patient by phone
GET {{baseUrl}}/lookup/patient/by-phone?phone=+15551234567
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Lookup patient by MRI
GET {{baseUrl}}/lookup/patient/by-mri?mri=MRI-001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------
### STAFF LOOKUP
### ----------------------------------------

### Lookup staff by staff number
GET {{baseUrl}}/lookup/staff/by-number?staffNumber=STF-001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Lookup staff by email
GET {{baseUrl}}/lookup/staff/by-email?email=doctor@example.com
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Lookup staff by user ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/lookup/staff/by-user-id?userId={{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

